channel.title: Hi there, it's Alessio
channel.description:
Hi guys, my name is Alessio, I live and work in Germany and I have been working on a consulting service for analytics and data. I love SQL tables but also the way computation is going (cloud + parallel). I have been crunching numbers as a profession for a little over 9 years now, first in finance then in BI/Analytics.
I still have a full time job and run the consulting as a side project.
